Buffett, Hamburg, Hambrick Named to Lubrizol Board After Buyout

-- B y   M a r y e l l e n   T i g h e
-- 
2011-09-21T14:18:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-21/buffett-hamburg-hambrick-named-to-lubrizol-board-after-buyout.html
Berkshire Hathaway Inc. (BRK/A)  named Chief
Executive Officer  Warren Buffett  and Chief Financial Officer
Marc Hamburg to the board of Lubrizol Corp., the additives maker
it acquired this month.  Lubrizol CEO  James Hambrick  will also be a director,
Wickliffe, Ohio-based Lubrizol said today in a regulatory
filing.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Maryellen Tighe in New York at 
 Mtighe6@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Kraut at   dkraut2@bloomberg.net  